        "text": "Deuteronomy 14:28",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). In the seventh year, which was Sabbatical, there would probably be no tithe, for there was to be no harvest. The profit of the earth was for all, and every one was free to eat at pleasure.",
